%head
  %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}
  %title WeLikeToTravel
  %meta{:content => "WeLikeToTravel is a web app to track the time and place of your life events.", :name => "description"}
  %meta{:content => "Jeraimee Hughes", :name => "author"}
  /[if lt IE 9]
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>

  %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}
  /
    CSS
    \==================================================
  %link{:href => "stylesheets/base.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
  %link{:href => "stylesheets/skeleton.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
  %link{:href => "stylesheets/layout.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
  /
    Favicons
    \==================================================
  %link{:href => "images/favicon.ico", :rel => "shortcut icon"}
  %link{:href => "images/apple-touch-icon.png", :rel => "apple-touch-icon"}
  %link{:href => "images/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png", :rel => "apple-touch-icon", :sizes => "72x72"}
  %link{:href => "images/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png", :rel => "apple-touch-icon", :sizes => "114x114"}
  = stylesheet_link_tag :application
  = javascript_include_tag :application
  = csrf_meta_tags


%body
  .container
    #sign_in.sixteen.columns
      %a(href = "#") Sign In
    #header.sixteen.columns
      %h1.remove-bottom WeLikeToTravel
      %h5 Version 0.1
    .sixteen.columns
      %hr
    .one-third.column
      %h3 What is WLTT?
      %p WeLikeToTravel is an application to track your location and share with your friends. Some real text needs to go here otherwise nobody will understand what the fuck we are doing.
    .one-third.column
      %h3 Another Column?
      %p Yep. I kind of like this 3 column under a large header idea. Here's some lipsum: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis ultricies mauris ut mauris bibendum feugiat. I hope that was OK to include that. I just thought a little more content in this column would be good to see.
    .one-third.column
      %h3 Recent Activity
      %ul.square
        %li
          %strong> NoOne InParticular
          \: "OMG! This is exactly what I need!!"
        %li
          %strong> A. Famous Person
          \: "Now the papparazzi will know where (and when) I was!"
        %li
          %strong> You
          \: "Get on with it, already."
    .sixteen.columns
      %hr.remove-top.remove-bottom
    %footer.sixteen.columns
      - now = Time.new
      %p.remove-top.remove-bottom
        &copy; Copyright
        = now.year
        Jeraimee Hughes / WLTT
  /
    JS
    \==================================================
  %script{:src => "javascripts/tabs.js"}
  /
    End Document
    \==================================================

